application_type_full: Outline planning permission: Some matters reserved
description: Redevelopment for residential development comprising not more than 74 dwellings at a density of not less than 30 dph (including 50% affordable housing) together with public open space, play provision and facilities for sports and recreation together with associated infrastructure
decision_conditions: The site is not previously developed land within the urban area and its development for housing is contrary to PPG3, Adopted Policy and Policy 1.1 and Chapter 5 (Housing) of the Council's Replacement Unitary Development Plan. | The site forms part of land designated Community Open Space for the purposes of the Council's Replacement Unitary Development Plan and as such the development is contrary to policies OL10A, OL12 and OL14 of the adopted UDP and policies 3.4 and 3.5 of the Council's Replacement UDP.
